    "Worms' speed and autonomy make them hazardous, causing internet interruptions and severe financial harm to afflicted organisations and individuals.",
    "Spyware secretly tracks users' internet activities, keystrokes (keyloggers), and financial data.",
    "It may be installed without the user's knowledge via free software downloads or malicious websites.",
    "Identity theft and unauthorised access to personal and financial data may result from spyware, which slows system performance and internet connections.When run, viruses change other computer programmes and implant their own code.",
    "Infected systems may malfunction, lose data, and operate poorly."
